(Pasta size: Grap them and should see the size of 500 Won coin)


Spaghetti aglio e olio
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GG86sJrYWKo
- Cook Spaghetti (Add Salt)
- Olive Oil on Pan. Add Sliced Garlic, Chopped Hot Pepper, Chopped Parsely, 1 Ladle of pasta water, Generous amount of pepper
- Add Spaghetti and mix for 3 min.
- Add Chopped Parsely and serve


Spaghetti Carbonara
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=on_hoRfpX44
- Cook Spaghetti (Add Salt)
- Mix Three Eggs + Lots of pepper + Lots of Grated Parmesan Cheese
- Olive Oil on Pan. Add Cut Pork Belly (Not too crispy), 1 Ladle of pasta water
- Add Spaghetti and Egg Mix


Fettuccine Alfredo
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TLbsMcsZsiM&list=PLcApjfOBgcUpMonDa_8K3fe8E5078uGzW&index=2&t=0s
- Cook Fettuce (Add Salt)
- 1 Ladle of pasta water on pan
- Add a chuck of Butter and mix on low heat until melted
- Put pasta and Grated Parmesan Cheese. Mix them


Onion Cheesy spaghetti
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fO8cnA-4sAk&list=PLcApjfOBgcUpMonDa_8K3fe8E5078uGzW&index=58
- Cook Spaghetti (Add Salt)
- Olive Oil on Pan. Add Sliced Onions (Cooked until brown), 1 Ladle of pasta water, a slice of butter
- Put pasta and Grated Parmesan Cheese. Mix them


Tuna spaghetti with capers and fresh tomato
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdDzYW6dxFs&list=PLcApjfOBgcUpMonDa_8K3fe8E5078uGzW&index=54
- Cook Spaghetti (Add Salt)
- Olive Oil on Pan. Add Sliced Garlic, Chopped Hot Pepper, Cut Cherry Tomato, white wine, canned tuna
- Add Salt and chopped parsely


Fettuccine
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vziTZ3M0Mbs&list=PLcApjfOBgcUpMonDa_8K3fe8E5078uGzW&index=52
- Cook Fettuce (Add Salt)
- Olive Oil on Pan. Add Chopped Hot Pepper, Minced Garlic, white wine, A chunk of butter
- Put Fettuce and Add Grated Parmesan Cheese, chopped parsely, 1 Ladle of pasta water


Garlic Basil Chicken Breasts with Spaghetti
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wZuqPJg4RtI
- Cook Spaghetti (Add Salt)
- Salt + Pepper on Chicken Breast
- Olive Oil on Pan. Grill Chicken. Add butter and Minced Garlic later
- Put 1 diced tomato, tomato paste, 1/2 glass of white wine, 1 Ladle of pasta water, Salt, Pepper, Chopped Basil, and Pasta


Chicken a la King with an Italian twist
Salt on Boiling water + Fettuce
Pan + Butter + Sliced Chicken Breast + Oregano + Salt + Minced Garlic => Mix => Set aside
Pan + Butter + Sliced Mushroom + Diced Red Onion + Sliced Red Pepper + Sliced Green Pepper + a spoon of flour => Mix => Return Chicken with Juices + cup of red wine + cup of Chicken Stock + Salt + Pepper => Mix => Add a 3-4 spoons of cream and simmer for 2 mins


Chicken Francaise (Fransess)
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lw7EixBGu60
Two eggs + Salt + Pepper + 1/2 Chopped Parsely + Grated Parmesan Cheese => Mix
Chicken breast buttlyfly cut & flattened in wrap
Pan + olive oil + a slice of butter
Chicken on flour, then on egg mix. 4 mins each side. Set them aside after
1/2 cup of dry white wine + chicken stock + small spoon of garlic + 1/2 lemon juice => Reduce (and put remaining 1/2 Chopped Parsely + a slice of butter) => Mix well
Return Chicken




Fried Rice
- cool down rice to remove stickiness
- put rice + 1 tbsp oyster sauce + 1 tbsp cooking oil + green onion on egg pool
- cooking oil + green onion stir fry
